data.description: This inviting 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is nestled in the highly sought-after Buckhead Manor neighborhood, just moments away from the vibrant heart of downtown Madison. Situated on a spacious and level corner lot, this residence offers both convenience and tranquility. The generous four bedrooms provide ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests, while the 2.5 baths ensure that daily routines run smoothly. With its prime location, well-maintained surroundings, and spacious interior, this home embodies the ideal suburban retreat in the heart of Madison's charming Buckhead Manor neighborhood.
